AUDIO: 'Firefly use it and a number of the other video generators do as well. Don\'t have a problem with that at all. So, all that said, it will be rolling out to more countries they have said with expansion'

[02:20] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'over time. I\'m hearing weeks, but I\'ve heard a lot of things over the last few months. Now, can you get around that region lock with a VPN? I mean, I don\'t know, maybe. But it also might just be'

[02:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'worth saving a headache and waiting a little bit to see when API or larger access rolls out. So, despite the rumors that SeaDance 2.0 had been canceled, that I mean, that was never true. We'

